functions.label: DatePickerContextProvider
description: React Component that acts as a wrapper for DatePickerContext.

functions.label: FullTimeRangeSelector
description:
Component for rendering a button which automatically sets the range of the time filter
to the time range of data in the index(es) mapped to the supplied Kibana data view or query.

functions.label: getTimeFilterRange
description: Function to get the time filter range as timestamps.

functions.label: useRefresh
description: Provides the latest refresh, both manual or auto.

functions.label: useRefreshIntervalUpdates
description: Custom hook to return refresh interval updates from the `refreshIntervalObservable$` observable.

functions.label: useTimefilter
description: Custom hook to get the timefilter from runtime dependencies.

functions.label: useTimeRangeUpdates
description: Custom hook to return time range updates from the `timeChangeObservable$` observable.

interfaces.label: DatePickerDependencies
description: Date Picker Dependencies to be passed on via `DatePickerContextProvider`.
